  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A REDUCTION IN C-SECTION RATES USING THE HEM-AVERT速 PERIANAL STABILIZER.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study is being conducted to evaluate an existing FDA approved device called the
      HEM-AVERT速 Perianal Stabilizer for its efficacy in reducing Cesarean births and/or reducing
      the second stage of labor.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
